  <entry>
    <title>ISCTF-可爱的emoji</title>
    <link href="https://jawiiki.github.io/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E5%8F%AF%E7%88%B1%E7%9A%84emoji/"/>
    <id>https://jawiiki.github.io/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E5%8F%AF%E7%88%B1%E7%9A%84emoji/</id>
    <published>2022-11-02T07:34:35.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-11-02T07:59:57.424Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>下载附件，压缩包加压需要密码</p><p>根据提示</p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E5%8F%AF%E7%88%B1%E7%9A%84emoji/image-20221031173733076-16672285714621.png" alt="image-20221031173733076"></p><p>判断其爆破类型为掩码爆破，输入掩码KEY?????</p><p>获得解压密码</p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E5%8F%AF%E7%88%B1%E7%9A%84emoji/image-20221031173849894.png" alt="image-20221031173849894"></p><p>压缩包内txt含有一堆emoji表情，数量不多，猜测可能是某种编码，上网搜索到emoji-aes</p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E5%8F%AF%E7%88%B1%E7%9A%84emoji/image-20221031174045396.png" alt="image-20221031174045396"></p><p>发现解码需要一个KEY，联系解压时的KEYIS”AES”，推测这里的KEY应该是AES,初试解码失败，尝试修改Rotation中数字，发现a&#x3D;图案对应变换，逐个尝试，联系提示2中</p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E5%8F%AF%E7%88%B1%E7%9A%84emoji/image-20221031174330738.png" alt="image-20221031174330738"></p><p>发现当输入数字9时，图案变为emoji中第一个图案，得出flag：</p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E5%8F%AF%E7%88%B1%E7%9A%84emoji/image-20221031174457698.png" alt="image-20221031174457698"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
