    <id>https://jawiiki.github.io/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E8%BF%9B%E6%9D%A5%E8%A2%AB%E9%AA%97%EF%BC%81/</id>
    <published>2022-11-02T07:33:07.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-11-02T07:59:48.086Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>解压后是一个ppt，打开是一张图片<img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E8%BF%9B%E6%9D%A5%E8%A2%AB%E9%AA%97%EF%BC%81/image-20221102120029584.png" alt="image-20221102120029584"></p><p>ppt是可以理解成一个压缩包，解压后发现音乐’你被骗了‘</p><p>拖入audacity中，发现奇怪音频</p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E8%BF%9B%E6%9D%A5%E8%A2%AB%E9%AA%97%EF%BC%81/image-20221102120128466.png" alt="image-20221102120128466"></p><p>类似于拨号音DTMF，网上搜索自动解码工具<img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E8%BF%9B%E6%9D%A5%E8%A2%AB%E9%AA%97%EF%BC%81/image-20221102120243276.png" alt="image-20221102120243276"></p><hr><p>解出一组数据</p><p>125 122 146 124 150 130 234 144 100 164 226 66 210 201 203 45 236</p><p>无法解出，怀疑进制转换，仅出现最大数6，应为七进制</p><p>转为10进制后</p><p>68 65 83 67 84 70 123 81 49 95 118 48 105 99 101 33 125</p><p>转换为ASCII码后<img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E8%BF%9B%E6%9D%A5%E8%A2%AB%E9%AA%97%EF%BC%81/image-20221102120435901.png" alt="image-20221102120435901"></p><p>得出flag</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
