  <entry>
    <title>ISCTF-酱紫乱</title>
    <link href="https://jawiiki.github.io/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E9%85%B1%E7%B4%AB%E4%B9%B1/"/>
    <id>https://jawiiki.github.io/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E9%85%B1%E7%B4%AB%E4%B9%B1/</id>
    <published>2022-11-02T07:32:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-11-02T07:59:43.866Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E9%85%B1%E7%B4%AB%E4%B9%B1/image-20221101101012662.png" alt="image-20221101101012662"></p><p>打开后，每个文本一个字，写脚本整合</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">2896</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&quot;./%d.txt&quot;</span>%i,encoding=<span class="string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">        a+=f.read()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&quot;./temp.txt&quot;</span>,<span class="string">&quot;w&quot;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">    f.write(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E9%85%B1%E7%B4%AB%E4%B9%B1/image-20221101101056844.png" alt="image-20221101101056844"></p><p>得出一串乱码，拖入CyberChef，base解码</p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E9%85%B1%E7%B4%AB%E4%B9%B1/image-20221101100901462.png" alt="image-20221101100901462"></p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E9%85%B1%E7%B4%AB%E4%B9%B1/image-20221101101140482.png" alt="image-20221101101140482"></p><p>得到一串不知道什么的东西，各种解码都无效，且所要的数据均有出现,如<code>&#123;</code>,<code>&#125;</code></p><p>怀疑是按字出现的频率排序</p><hr><p>统计各数字出现的频率</p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E9%85%B1%E7%B4%AB%E4%B9%B1/image-20221101100917065.png" alt="image-20221101100917065"></p><p><img src="/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E9%85%B1%E7%B4%AB%E4%B9%B1/image-20221101100922160.png" alt="image-20221101100922160"></p><p>思路正确，得出flag ISCTF{so_cLut73r}</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/2022/11/02/ISCTF-%E9%85%B1%E7%B4%AB%E4%B9%B1/image-20221101101012662.png&quot; alt=&quot;image-20221101101012662&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;打开后，每个文本一个字，写脚</summary>
      
    
    
    
